{"tid":1863760,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[ 行動方向 ] 基於政府把關不力 香港已進入病毒潛藏社區階段","createTime":"2020-02-05T09:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T17:42:12.000Z","uid":138964,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed74387559bf4fcf13e7d3b02b98a7bccc28ed2","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">病毒前題</span><br />\n+ 7日左右潛藏 <br />\n+ 帶毒者未發病亦可傳播病毒 <br />\n<br />\n4/2 【武漢肺炎】威院25歲男確診 成港最年輕患者 住九龍城近期冇外遊<br />\n5/2 25歲新田圍病者星期日與人有接觸<br />\n5/2 遊輪病人<br />\n<br />\n表示香港已進入病毒潛藏社區階段<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">病毒傳播途徑</span><br />\n<br />\n社區 : 公共交通工具 ( 飛機 , 巴士 , 小巴 , 地鐵 ,中港巴 )<br />\n家居 : 排水口 ( 隔氣乾塘引致病毒經氣體由水管進入家居 )<br />\n個人 : 經常接觸的地方 (e.g. 人與人傾計口沫 , 接觸大門把手 , 電話)<br />\n<br />\n個人&amp;家居預防<br />\n- 口罩<br />\n- 勤洗手 消毒<br />\n- 家居去水常注水 ( 水 1: 49 漂白水 最理想 )<br />\n<br />\n社區及文宣工作<br />\n- 每層LIFT 口位可以文宣 社區防疫工作<br />\n- 議員區民檢疫站 ( 組隊同路人 組織人員/物資 優先處理香港人 )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">盡量堵截源頭行動方向</span><br />\n<br />\n交通篇<br />\n* 所有公共交通運輸公司 應該制定標準定時 清潔車廂 <br />\n* 如公司未能提供 安全工作環境 司機應與工會聯絡如何解決 。或者考慮停駛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">( 司機你每日送咁多人上車 如果公司配合唔到防疫工作 你就係傳播病毒既幫兇 )</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國際篇 ( 鍵盤戰士向 )<br />\n<br />\n1. 請求美國CDC、軍方醫療船派遣人員到香港<br />\n白宮聯署，請求美國CDC、軍方醫療船派遣人員到香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1859122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1859122</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 要求 香港國際遊說團 向各國領事 要求嚴厲檢驗香港人入境<br />\n香港已經潛藏大量生化人, 我地香港人 已經同 腥港人 已經打成一片<br />\n要國際揮劍 我地就要做國際既眼"},{"pid":"7dab96a8c29e9e8f89838fdebe712e2cba750705","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"玩左咁耐X登<br />\n我都想試下20連好耐"},{"pid":"1d13346cb656c6152512f89532136cb8dc829b69","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n各路手足 提供多啲意見出黎"},{"pid":"50ad17a8df1af9c0fba8f3678804d3ba3a943e78","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46b4199fcfa4d6d511a45699d2eca0488895cb0","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"4<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58018de2987431eafaefd41a421e1e3f1420ad6a","tid":1863760,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62194b42a17d1bf8eb3179e9b93cb2d536eb535","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都好鐘意聽林鄭鳩嗡之後網上炮轟一個稻草人"},{"pid":"ba181c36349cd20bb7f4b91c5281de113a0a1454","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c237f93151809367863c4317d31dae680ffd77","tid":1863760,"uid":6741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25e9e0f5d6f4952de17a80a2a74233203073634a","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"經濟圈方面<br />\n店主除左做好啲<br />\n聯網做防疫物資<br />\n我都冇野好補充了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5d73f85be6ba4fe74226758f146e8e2c34b535","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"[飛起中國WHO] 新冠病毒疫情危機：G7將開會共商對策<br />\n<br />\n香港人要嬴 香港都應該都要收到G7 風"},{"pid":"5190edadebdbfc3c3034c8fca24faa12ce84ed8c","tid":1863760,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite